<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>Not much to say about <a href="/when-it-s-too-late-to-go-back">The only way left to go is forward</a> besides that this is, in part, the spiritual rewrite to <a href="/aftermath">Aftermath</a> I've wanted to create for a long time. Part of the greater MacCanon. I might revisit other, more Aftermath-like stories in this same setting; there's a lot of imagery I neglected to use for this story but feel would fit the same melancholy I was shooting for in both Aftermath and this.</p>
<p>Recommended Listening is <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B7xai5u_tnk">&quot;Monody&quot; by TheFatRat (featuring Laura Brehm)</a>.</p>
